    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "This gremlin\u2019s head and pointed ears are overlarge compared to the rest of its anatomy. Thin, often matted hair tops a drexin\u2019s scalp. Its light-starved, wizened flesh stretches taut across its bones, and its claws brush the ground as it walks. An average drexin stands 3 feet tall and weighs 25 pounds."
        }
    ],
    "html": "<i>This pale, spindly creature has a vaguely humanoid shape, but with arms unnaturally long for its torso. Strands of long white hair sprout from its bulbous head, and its eyes are pools of liquid darkness.</i>",
